{"id":11122,"date":"2022-02-11T14:51:11","date_gmt":"2022-02-11T12:51:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/?p=11122"},"modified":"2022-02-11T14:51:11","modified_gmt":"2022-02-11T12:51:11","slug":"chairperson-to-embark-on-outreach-visits-to-the-regions","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/chairperson-to-embark-on-outreach-visits-to-the-regions\/","title":{"rendered":"Chairperson to Embark on Outreach Visits to the Regions"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Pamela Mate<\/p>\n<p>The Chairperson of the National Council, Hon. Lukas Sinimbo Muha, will be conducting regional visits to the Otjozondjupa and Kavango East regions from Monday, 14 February to Saturday, 27 February 2022. The regional visits by the Office of the Chairperson forms part of Outreach Programme activities as set out in the National Council 2017\/2018 \u2013 2021\/2022 Strategic Plan and aims to enhance public and key stakeholder participation in the legislative process.<\/p>\n<p>The objective of the regional visits is to create awareness about the review and oversight role of the National Council; engage key stakeholders in the regions to increase public understanding of the House of Parliament; and improve the perception of the public on the work of the National Council and its Members.<\/p>\n<p>Hon. Muha\u2019s regional visits commenced in the Zambezi region in October 2021. The public participation initiative will start with a courtesy call on the Governor of the Otjozondjupa region, and will see the Chairperson visit traditional authorities, youth groups and community and members across various towns in the Otjozondjupa region, including Otjiwarongo, Okakarara, Grootfontein and Tsumkwe.<\/p>\n<p>Community Members are encouraged to attend the meetings and participate in the law-making process as per the schedule below. A full programme for week two in the Kavango East region will be provided in due course.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<table width=\"756\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"180\"><strong>DATE<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"197\"><strong>09H00 SESSION<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"150\"><strong>11H00 SESSION<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"229\"><strong>15H00 SESSION<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"180\">Monday, 14 Feb 2022<\/td>\n<td width=\"197\">Courtesy Call on the Governor<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Office of the Governor<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>OTJIWARONGO<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"150\">GK Wahl Primary School<\/p>\n<p><strong>OTJIWARONGO<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"229\">Community Meeting<\/p>\n<p>Venue: \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <strong>NDC Tourism Centre<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>OTJIWARONGO<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"180\">Tuesday, 15 Feb 2022<\/td>\n<td width=\"197\">Courtesy Call on the Traditional Authority<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Kambazembi Office<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>OKAKARARA<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"150\">Youth Groups<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Pamue Hall<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>OKAKARARA<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"229\">Waterberg Secondary School \/ Okakarara Secondary School<\/p>\n<p>Venue:\u00a0 <strong>Waterberg Dining Hall<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>OKAKARARA<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"180\">Thursday, 17 Feb 2022<\/td>\n<td width=\"197\">Courtesy Call on the Mayor of Grootfontein<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Grootfontein Constituency \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Office<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>GROOTFONTEIN<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"150\">Community Meeting<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Showground Hall<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>GROOTFONTEIN<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"229\">&nbsp;<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"180\">Friday, 18 Feb 2022<\/td>\n<td width=\"197\">Courtesy Call on the Traditional Authority<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Boardroom TA<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>TSUMKWE<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"150\">Tsumkwe Secondary School<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/td>\n<td width=\"229\">Community Meeting<\/p>\n<p>Venue: <strong>Community Hall<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>TSUMKWE<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Pamela Mate The Chairperson of the National Council, Hon. Lukas Sinimbo Muha, will be conducting regional visits to the Otjozondjupa and Kavango East regions from Monday, 14 February to Saturday, 27 February 2022. The regional visits by the Office of the Chairperson forms part of Outreach Programme activities as set out in the National Council&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":8,"featured_media":5589,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[159,39],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-11122","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-home-page-slider","category-news","category-159","category-39","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11122","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/8"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11122"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11122\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":11123,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11122\/revisions\/11123"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5589"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11122"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\